  "description": "<p><em>Looking for a </em><em><strong>first job</strong></em><em> or </em><em><strong>taking a year gap </strong></em><em>/ </em><em><strong>mid-career switch</strong></em><em> that’s </em><em><strong>more than </strong></em><em>just a </em><em><strong>desk and a title?</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Gain a </em><em><strong>hands-on experience</strong></em><em> on events &amp; marketing ,</em><em><strong>grabbing</strong></em><em> more opportunites for </em><em><strong>growth</strong></em><em> &amp; </em><em><strong>networking !</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Be A Boss Of Yourself Here ! TAKE A LEAD!</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Your Role :</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support &amp; generate leads for the clients</li>\n  <li>Raise awareness for the clients</li>\n  <li>Engage 1-1 with the customers</li>\n  <li>Assist in planning and managing</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Offers :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1-1 Mentorship provided <em><strong>(No Experience Needed)</strong></em></li>\n  <li>Opportunity to travel international &amp; regional to expand growth,learning</li>\n  <li>Hangouts &amp; team-bonding sessions</li>\n  <li>Career progressions within the industry <em><strong>( performance based )</strong></em></li>\n  <li>Extra bonuses</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Search:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fast learner</li>\n  <li>Curious &amp; wanting for more</li>\n  <li>Willing to go the extra mile</li>\n  <li>Driven &amp; goal - oriented</li>\n  <li>Independent &amp; can work in a team</li>\n  <li>Love talking to people &amp; have fun</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>If you’re </em><em><strong>full</strong></em><em> of </em><em><strong>ideas</strong></em><em>, </em><em><strong>energy</strong></em><em>, and </em><em><strong>ambition</strong></em><em>. This is your chance to do meaningful work, meet inspiring people, and </em><em><strong>build a career</strong></em><em> you’re proud of ~ </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW!</strong></em>